194599 2When, in like manner, any cantonment ceases to be a cantonment and the local area comprised therein is not immediately placed under the control of a local authority, the balance of the cantonment fund and other property vesting in the 3 Board] shall vest in Government, and the liabilities of the 3 Board] shall be transferred to the 4 Central Government].
