126827 8Application of funds and property transferred under sections 6 and 7.- Any cantonment fund or portion of a cantonment fund or other property of a 1 Board] vesting in Government under the provisions of section 6 or section 7 shall be applied in the first place to satisfy any liabilities of the 1 Board] transferred under such provisions to the 2 Central Government], and in the second place for the benefit of the inhabitants of the local area which has ceased to be a cantonment or, as the case may be, part of a cantonment.
